# .cursor/rules/gold-ticker-live.mdc

## Project Identity
GoldTickerLive — bilingual (EN/AR) static gold pricing platform for GCC/Arab markets.
Vanilla ES6, zero external JS dependencies, GitHub Pages hosted.

## Sacred Invariants (NEVER change these values)
- AED peg: 3.6725
- Troy ounce: 31.1035g
- Karat purity values in src/config/karats.js
- Pricing formula in src/lib/price-calculator.js

## Architecture Rules
- All user-visible text: src/config/translations.js (EN + AR keys)
- RTL must work on everything
- CSS custom properties for all colors/spacing/typography
- New components: src/components/
- Shared utilities: src/lib/
- No external JS dependencies — ever
- CSS animations only (no JS animation libraries)
- npm test must pass at every commit

## Session Protocol
- Read @docs/plans/README.md and @REVAMP_PLAN.md before planning
- Write session plan in docs/plans/ if scope > 5 files
- Commit after each logical change (max 3 files between commits)
- git checkpoint before multi-file refactors
- At end: npm test + npm run validate + npm run build — all green
- Update REVAMP_PLAN.md with new section
- Open PR with clear summary

## Quality Standards
- No placeholder comments — complete or skip
- No "Loading..." text — use .skeleton CSS
- Every animation: prefers-reduced-motion media query
- All interactive elements: min 44px touch targets
- All prices: tabular-nums, freshness labels visible
- Focus states on every interactive element
- Zero broken internal links




